import { StyleSheet,Dimensions } from "react-native";
import React, { useState } from 'react';

const width = Dimensions.get('window').width;
const height = Dimensions.get('window').height;



export const colors = {
    
    primary:{
        white: '#ffffff',
        default: '#D3DDDF',
        defaultlight: '#eff3f4',
        defaultdark: '#ADBBBD',
        red: '#FF6347',
        orange: '#ffa500',
        yellow: '#ffff00',
        yellowgreen: '#9acd32',
        green: '#2e8b57',
        turquoise: '#afeeee',
        royalblue: '#4169e1',
        lightblue: '#ADD8E6',
        blue: '#007AFF',
        lavender: '#e6e6fa',
        purple: '#ba55d3',
        magenta: '#c71585',

        beige: '#ffebcd',
        gray: '#d3d3d3',  
        black: '#000000',
        tungstene: '#2c3e50',
        transparent: '#000000',
    },
    pale:{
        white: '#ffffff',
        default: '#eff3f4',
        defaultlight: '#ffffff',
        defaultdark: '#D3DDDF',
        red: '#FFC9BF',
        orange: '#FFDEA0',
        yellow: '#FFFFBC',

        purple: '#F9E2FF',
        magenta: '#FFDEF3',
        pink: '#FFECF0',
        brown: '#FFD9C6',
        beige: '#FFF8EF',
        gray: '#F2F2F2',  
        black: '#828282',
        transparent: '#ffffff',
    }
    
};
export const container = StyleSheet.create({
    
    container: {
        flex:1,
        alignContent: 'center',
        justifyContent: 'center',
    },
    header: {
        width: width,
        height: 150,
        alignContent: 'center',
        justifyContent: 'center',
        alignItems: 'center',
        flexDirection: 'row',
    },
    body: {
        flex:1,
        alignContent: 'center',
        justifyContent: 'flex-start',
        alignItems: 'center',
    },
    subcategory: {
        width: width,
        height: 45,
        borderBottomWidth: 1,
        borderBottomColor: 'gray',
        justifyContent: 'center',
    },
    subcategorytext: {
        marginLeft: 20,
        fontSize: 16,
        color: 'black',
        textAlignVertical: 'center',
    },
    headerdate: {
        fontSize: 14,
        fontFamily: 'AvenirNextCondensed-Regular',
        shadowRadius: 5,
        shadowOpacity: 1,
        shadowColor: colors.primary.white,
        shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 0 },
    },
    headertitle: {
        fontSize: 20,
        fontFamily: 'AvenirNextCondensed-Regular',
        shadowRadius: 5,
        shadowOpacity: 1,
        shadowColor: colors.primary.white,
        shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 0 },
    },
    button: {
        height:40,
        width: width-20,
        borderWidth:1,
        borderColor: colors.primary.blue,
        borderRadius: 10,
        backgroundColor: colors.primary.default,
        justifyContent: 'center',
        alignItems: 'center',
        margin:10,
    },
    buttontext:{
        fontSize: 16,
        color: colors.black,
    },
    modal:{
        width: "70%",
        backgroundColor: colors.primary.defaultlight,
        borderColor: colors.primary.black,
        borderWidth: 1,
        borderRadius: 10,
        justifyContent: 'center',
        alignItems: 'center',
        padding: 20,
        shadowColor: colors.primary.black,
        shadowRadius: 5,
        shadowOffset: { width: 5, height: 5 },
        shadowOpacity: 0.2,
    },
    textinput: {
        width:width*0.9,
        borderWidth: 1,
        borderRadius: 10,
        height:40,
        borderColor: colors.primary.black,
        paddingHorizontal:10,
        backgroundColor: 'white',
    },
    section:{
        width: "100%",
        height:40,
        justifyContent: 'center',
        alignItems: 'flex-start',
        paddingHorizontal: 10,
        borderBottomWidth:1,
        borderBottomColor: colors.primary.gray,
    },
    tasktext: {
        textAlign:'left',
        marginLeft: 5,
        textAlignVertical: 'center',
    },
    taskcontainer: {
        width: '100%',
        flexDirection: 'row',
        height: 40,
        alignContent: 'center',
        alignItems: 'center',
        justifyContent: 'flex-start',
        backgroundColor: 'white',
        paddingLeft: 10,
        borderBottomColor: colors.pale.gray,
        borderBottomWidth: 1,
    },
    checkbox: {
        width: 25,
        height: 25,
        borderWidth: 1,
        borderColor: 'black',
        marginLeft: 30,
    },
    analytics:{
        height:80,
        borderColor: colors.primary.gray,
        borderWidth:1,
        borderRadius:10,
        margin:10,
        backgroundColor: colors.primary.white,
        padding:10
    },
    setting:{
        width: "100%",
        height:50,
        flexDirection: 'row',
        justifyContent: 'flex-start',
        alignItems: 'center',
        backgroundColor: colors.primary.white,
        paddingHorizontal: 10,

    },
    statTitle:{
        width: "100%",

        flexDirection: 'row',
        justifyContent: 'center',
        alignItems: 'center',
        backgroundColor: colors.primary.white,

    settingsArrow: {

    },

        width: width/4,

        borderTopLeftRadius: 20,
        borderTopRightRadius: 20,
    },
    tabtext: {
        fontSize: 14,
        color: colors.primary.black,
        fontFamily: 'AvenirNextCondensed-Regular',
    },
    block: {
        width: "90%",
        height: height-170-150-28,
        alignContent: 'center',
        justifyContent: 'center',
    },
    listblock:{
        flex:1,
        alignContent: 'center',
        justifyContent: 'flex-start',
        width:'100%',
        borderTopColor: colors.primary.black, 
        shadowColor: colors.primary.black,
        shadowOpacity: 0.2,
        shadowRadius: 5,
        shadowOffset: { width: 2, height: 5 },
        borderBottomLeftRadius: 20,
        borderBottomRightRadius: 20,
        borderTopWidth: 0.5,
    },
    color: {
        width: 30,
        height: 30,
        borderWidth: 1,
        borderRadius: 15,
        borderColor: 'lightgray',
        margin: 5,
        justifyContent: 'center',
        alignItems: 'center',
    },
    statblock:{
        backgroundColor: colors.primary.white,
        borderRadius: 10,
        borderWidth: 1,
        borderColor: colors.primary.gray,
        shadowColor: colors.primary.black,
        shadowOpacity: 0.2,
        shadowRadius: 5,
        shadowOffset: { width: 2, height: 5 },
        flexDirection: 'row',
        justifyContent: 'space-evenly',
        alignContent:'space-between',
        padding:10,
        margin:5,
    },
    keyNumber:{
        fontSize: 30,
        fontWeight: 'bold',
        fontFamily: 'AvenirNextCondensed-Regular',
        color: colors.primary.black,
    },
    newModal:{
        height:100, 
        backgroundColor:colors.pale.default, 
        shadowColor:colors.primary.black, 
        shadowOpacity:0.2, 
        shadowOffset:{ height: -10 }, 
        shadowRadius:20,
        width:width,
    }
});



export const paleColor = (color) => {
  // Extract the base color and pale color group name (e.g., "white" and "primary" from "#ffffff")
  const colorGroup = color==undefined? colors.primary.default.substring(1) : color.substring(1); // Remove the '#' symbol
  const baseColor = Object.keys(colors.primary).find((key) => colors.primary[key] === `#${colorGroup}`);

  // If the base color is found, get its corresponding paler color from the "pale" sub-object
  if (baseColor && colors.pale[baseColor]) {
    return colors.pale[baseColor];
  }

  // If the base color is not found or there's no paler color, return the default color
  return colors.primary.defaultlight;
};
